<section class="rbp-membership-model" aria-label="Membership operating model">
  <div class="rbp-membership-model__inner page-width">
    <div class="rbp-membership-model__intro">
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__eyebrow">Membership operating model</div>
      <h2>Account-based membership access with subscription-ready pathways</h2>
      <p>New Customer Accounts are enabled. Premium Membership access uses lifecycle customer tags such as <strong>rbp-premium-applied</strong>, <strong>rbp-premium-approved</strong> and <strong>rbp-premium-active</strong>. Shopify Subscriptions can support membership billing, while manual business review remains required where applicable.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rbp-membership-model__grid">
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__card"><span>01</span><h3>Customer account pathway</h3><p>Members can use the customer account route for account details, orders and member pathway access.</p></div>
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__card"><span>02</span><h3>Lifecycle tags</h3><p>Customer tags identify application, approval, active and restricted Premium Membership states across member page logic.</p></div>
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__card"><span>03</span><h3>Subscription ready</h3><p>Shopify Subscriptions can support membership billing once final products, pricing and processes are confirmed.</p></div>
      <div class="rbp-membership-model__card"><span>04</span><h3>Operational support</h3><p>Manual checks, onboarding and member support may still be required for cases that need review.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
.rbp-membership-model{background:#f8fbff;padding:72px 0}.rbp-membership-model__inner{display:grid;gap:26px}.rbp-membership-model__intro{max-width:880px}.rbp-membership-model__eyebrow{display:inline-flex;border-radius:999px;background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8;padding:7px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}.rbp-membership-model h2{margin:14px 0 0;color:#0f172a;font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,50px);line-height:1.06;letter-spacing:-.035em;font-weight:900}.rbp-membership-model p{margin:14px 0 0;color:#64748b;line-height:1.7;font-size:15px}.rbp-membership-model__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:18px}.rbp-membership-model__card{background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(15,23,42,.1);border-radius:24px;padding:22px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(15,23,42,.05)}.rbp-membership-model__card span{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:15px;background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:14px}.rbp-membership-model__card h3{margin:0 0 8px;color:#0f172a;font-size:18px;font-weight:900}.rbp-membership-model__card p{font-size:14px;margin:0}@media(max-width:989px){.rbp-membership-model__grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}}@media(max-width:749px){.rbp-membership-model{padding:54px 0}.rbp-membership-model__grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
